 Muhammad the son of ‘Abd Allah’; Peace be on you, O people of the house of belief and unity; Peace be on you, O helpers of the religion of Allah and helpers of His Prophet and his family.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "ASSALAAMO A’LAA RASOOLIL LAAHE ASSALAAMO A’LAA NABIYYIL LAAHE ASSALAAMO A’LAA MOHAMMADIBN NE A’BDIL LAAHE ASSALAAMO A’LAA AHLE BAYTEHIT TAAHEREENA ASSALAAMO A’LAYKUM AYYOHASH SHOHADAAA-UL MOAMENOONA ASSALAAMO A’LAYKUM YAA AHLA BAYTIL EEMAANE WAT TAWHEEDE.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی رَسُوْلِ اللهِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی نَبِیِّ اللهِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ عَبْدِ اللهِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی اَھْلِ بَیْتِہِ الطَّاہِرِیْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكُمْ اَیُّہَا الشُّہَدَآئُ الْمُؤْمِنُوْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكُمْ یَا اَھْلَ بَیْتِ الْاِیْمَانِ وَالتَّوْحِیْدِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012784, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be on you for the patience which you have exercised for what a wonderful abode that is! I bear witness that Allah has chosen you for His religion and chosen you for His Prophet. I also bear witness that you truly strove for Allah and defended the religion of Allah and His Prophet and you gave yourselves for him.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ASSALAAMO A’LAYKUM YAA ANSAARA DEENIL LAAHE WA ANSAARA RASOOLEHI SALLAL LAAHO A’LAYHE WA AALEHI WA SALLAMA SALAAMUN A’LAYKUM BEMAA SABARTUM FA-NE’MA U’QBAD DAARE ASH-HADO ANNAL LAAHA QADIKH TAARAKUM LEDEENEHI WAS TAFAAKUM LERASOOLEHI WA ASH-HADO ANNAKUM QAD JAAHADTUM FIL LAAHE HAQQA JEHAADEHI WA NASARTUM LE-DEENIL LAAHE WA SUNNATE RASOOLEHI WA JUDTUM BE-ANFOSEKUM DOONAHU.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكُمْ یَا اَنْصَارَ دِیْنِ اللهِ وَاَنْصَارَ رَسُوْلِہٖ صَلَّی اللهُ عَلَیْہِ وَآلِہٖ وَسَلَّمَ سَلَامٌ عَلَیْكُمْ بِمَا صَبَرْتُمْ فَنِعْمَ عُقْبَی الدَّارِ۔ اَشْہَدُ اَنَّ اللهَ قَدِ اخْتَارَكُمْ لِدِیْنِہٖ وَاصْطَفَاكُمْ لِرَسُوْلِہٖ۔ وَاَشْہَدُ اَنَّكُمْ قَدْ جَاہَدْتُمْ فِیْ اللهِ حَقَّ جِہَادِہٖ وَنَصَرْتُمْ لِدِیْنِ اللهِ وَسُنَّۃِ رَسُوْلِہٖ وَجُدْتُمْ بِاَنْفُسِكُمْ دُوْنَہٗ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012785, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "I bear witness that you were killed on the path of the Prophet of Allah so may Allah grant you the best reward of (your services to) His Prophet and for Islam and its followers. May Allah make us see your faces in places of His pleasure and His honor with the Messengers and the truthful ones and the martyrs and the upright ones; for they are the best friends.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "WA ASH-HADO ANNAKUM QOTILTUM A’LAA MINHAAJE RASOOLIL LAAHE SALLAL LAAHO A’LAYHE WA AALEHI WA SALLAMA FA-JA-ZAAKOMUL LAAHO A’N NABIYYEHI WA A’NIL ISLAAME WA AHLEHI AFZALAL JA-ZAAA-E WA A’RRAFANAA FEE MAHALLE RIZWAANEHI WA MAWZE-A’ IKRAAMEHI MA-A’N NABIYYEENA WAS SIDDEEQEENA WASH SHOHADAAA-E WAS SAALEHEENA WA HASONA OOLAAA-EKA RAFEEQAN.", "ArabicText1": "وَاَشْہَدُ اَنَّكُمْ قُتِلْتُمْ عَلٰی مِنْہَاجِ رَسُوْلِ اللهِ صَلَّی اللهُ عَلَیْہِ وَآلِہٖ وَسَلَّمَ فَجَزَاكُمُ اللهُ عَنْ نَبِیِّہٖ وَعَنِ الْاِسْلَامِ وَاَھْلِہٖ اَفْضَلَ الْجَزَآئِ وَعَرَّفَنَا فِیْ مَحَلِّ رِضْوَانِہٖ وَمَوْضِعِ اِكْرَامِہٖ مَعَ النَّبِیِّیْنَ وَالصِّدِّیْقِیْنَ وَالشُّہَدَآئِ وَالصَّالِحِیْنَ وَحَسُنَ اُوْلٰٓئِكَ رَفیْقًا۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGree