glishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "I bear witness that you are the party of Allah and that one who wages war against you wages war against Allah. I also bear witness that you are the close, victorious ones to Allah who are living in the proximity of their Lord and are being nourished. May the curse of Allah and the angels and all the people fall on those who killed you and may the peace, mercy and blessings of Allah be upon you all.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ASH-HADO ANNAKUM HIZBUL LAAHE WA ANNA MAN HAARABAKUM FAQAD HAARABAL LAAHO WA ANNAKUM LEMANIL MOQARRABEENAL FAAA-EZEENA ALLAZEENA HUM AHYAA-UN I’NDA RABBEHIM YURZAQOONA FA-A’LAA MAN QATALAKUM LA’NATUL LAAHE WAL MALAAA-EKATE WAN NAASE AJMA-E’ENA WAS SALAAMO A’LAYKUM WA RAHMATUL LAAHE WA BARAKAATOHU.", "ArabicText1": "اَشْہَدُ اَنَّكُمْ حِزْبُ اللهِ وَاَنَّ مَنْ حَارَبَكُمْ فَقَدْ حَارَبَ اللهُ وَاَنَّكُمْ لَمِنَ الْمُقَرَّبِیْنَ الْفَآئِزِیْنَ اَلَّذِیْنَ ہُمْ اَحْیَائٌ عِنْدَ رَبِّہِمْ یُرْزَقُوْنَ فَعَلٰی مَنْ قَتَلَكُمْ لَعْنَۃُ اللهِ وَالْمَلَآئِكَۃِ وَالنَّاسِ اَجْمَعِیْنَ وَالسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكُمْ وَرَحْمَۃُ اللهِ وَبَرَكَاتُہٗ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "Arab